quest.swordsman_progression_01.desc.0: - Show your best sword to the Sensei
quest.swordsman_progression_01.name: Road to becoming the Best Swordsman
quest.swordsman_progression_01.start: <%s> If you want to be trained here you'll need a strong blade to fight with. Show me your best blade you've got.
quest.swordsman_progression_01.strong_sw: <%s> This one will do for my training.
quest.swordsman_progression_01.weak_swor: <%s> That weapon is a joke. You'll need something stronger than that.
quest.swordsman_progression_02.name: Staying Alive
quest.swordsman_progression_02.start: <%s> Your first test will be to survive the night. Good luck.
quest.swordsman_progression_02.sunset_st: <%s> We're starting when the sun sets, you're free to do as you please until then.
quest.swordsman_progression_02.survived: <%s> Congratulations you've survived the night, let's proceed then.
quest.swordsman_progression_02.three_day: <%s> I was starting to wonder if you died out there. But nonetheless you did survive the night like asked.
quest.swordsman_progression_03.complete: <%s> Very good work there. I reckon that you have some talent with that sword.
quest.swordsman_progression_03.desc.0: - Kill 20 creatures or humans in the mountains
quest.swordsman_progression_03.name: Feel the Wind
quest.swordsman_progression_03.start: <%s> Let the real training commmence then. Show me how proficient you are with your blade, go to any mountainous area and kill 20 creatures.
quest.swordsman_progression_04.name: The Fruits of Training
quest.swordsman_progression_04.start: <%s> So you can kill things without a problem, congratulations, how well can you handle hitting you enemy with precision then ?
